		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Simple test - run Family Basic (2.0, 2.1, or 3.0) and try typing some text. If it shows up correctly, there's an error in your test ROM. If it shows up incorrectly, there's an error in your keyboard emulation code.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
